## Proposed Changes

### Backend — [backend/src/main.cpp](file:///c:/Users/Admin/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/freelance_platform/backend/src/main.cpp)

**New SQLite Tables (added to `initializeSchema()`):**

| Table | Fields |
|---|---|
| `messages` | id, project_id, sender_id, receiver_id, message, timestamp |
| `notifications` | id, project_id, sender_id, message, is_read, timestamp |
| `payments` | id, project_id, client_id, freelancer_id, amount, status, timestamp |

**Fix:** Clean up all git merge conflict markers. Keep the post-merge `>>>>>>>` version.

**New API Routes:**

| Route | Method | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `GET /api/projects/<id>/bids` | GET | Fetch bids for a project |
| `PUT /api/applications/<id>/accept` | PUT | Accept a bid |
| `PUT /api/applications/<id>/reject` | PUT | Reject a bid |
| `GET /api/messages/<projectId>` | GET | Fetch messages for a project |
| `POST /api/messages` | POST | Send a message |
| `GET /api/notifications/<userId>` | GET | Fetch notifications for user |
| `POST /api/notifications` | POST | Send notification to project freelancers |
| `GET /api/payments/<userId>` | GET | Fetch payments for client |
| `POST /api/payments` | POST | Create payment record |
| `PUT /api/payments/<id>/release` | PUT | Release payment |
| `GET /api/freelancers` | GET | All freelancers with score (Find Talent) |
| `GET /api/analytics/<userId>` | GET | Freelancer analytics data |
| `GET /api/client/dashboard/<userId>` | GET | Client dashboard stats (full DB) |

**Freelancer Score Formula (computed in backend):**
```
score = (completedProjects * 15) + (avgRating * 20) + (reliabilityScore * 0.3) + (skillCount * 5) + (studyYear * 10)
score = min(100, score)
```

